        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This large blue toadstool glimmers with soft, magical light similar to moonlight. The spots of white adorning the mushroom\u2019s cap glow ethereally, as if illuminated from the inside, shedding dim light in a 10-foot radius.",
